OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry day with variable amounts
OL,6,Fof cloud. Often rather cloudy over
OL,7,FShetland with the best of the sunshine
OL,8,Facross Orkney. Feeling warm in the
OL,9,Fsunshine with light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FMostly sunny start to the
OL,12,Fevening for Orkney but cloudier over
OL,13,FShetland. Cloud will also spread
OL,14,Fsoutheast across Orkney overnight.
OL,15,
OL,16,CTuesday:FA cloudy morning with the odd
OL,17,Fspot of drizzle in places. Cloud
OL,18,Fbreaking up during the afternoon with
OL,19,Fsunny spells developing. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
